00362                                             push ds
00363                                             xor ax, ax
00364                                             mov ds, ax

00424                                           ;; init vga card
00425 0109           E8         3465              call init_vga_card
00426                                           ;; init basic bios vars
00427 010C           E8         34C1              call init_bios_area
00428                                           ;; init vbe functions
00429 010F           E8         93B3              call vbe_init
00430                                           ;; set int10 vect
00431                                             SET_INT_VECTOR(0x10, #0xC000, #vgabios_int10_handler)
 +a   0112           1E                           push ds
 +a   0113           31C0                         xor ax, ax
 +a   0115           8ED8                         mov ds, ax
 +a   0117           B8                   0133    mov ax,  #vgabios_int10_handler
 +a   011A           A3         0040              mov 0x10*4, ax
 +a   011D           B8                   C000    mov ax,  #0xC000
 +a   0120           A3         0042              mov 0x10*4+2, ax
 +a   0123           1F                           pop ds
00432                                           ;; display splash screen
00433 0124           E8         34FD              call _display_splash_screen
00434                                           ;; init video mode and clear the screen
00435 0127           B8                   0003    mov ax,#0x0003
00436 012A           CD                     10    int #0x10
00437                                           ;; show info
00438 012C           E8         34F6              call _display_info
00439                                           ;; show vbe info
00440 012F           E8         93C1              call vbe_display_info
00441 0132           CB                           retf

00448 0134           06                           push es

00450 0136           60                           pusha

00453 013C           E8         352B              call _int10_debugmsg
00454 013F           61                           popa
00455 0140           1F                           pop ds
00456 0141           07                           pop es

00458 0145           75           06              jne int10_test_1A

00460 014A           E9         00BC              jmp int10_end

00518 01C5           3C                     03    cmp al, #0x03
00519 01C7           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_05
00520 01C9           E8         9900              call vbe_biosfn_return_current_mode
00521 01CC           EB           3B              jmp int10_end
00522                       000001CE            int10_test_vbe_05:
00523 01CE           3C                     05    cmp al, #0x05
00524 01D0           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_06
00525 01D2           E8         9BF2              call vbe_biosfn_display_window_control
00526 01D5           EB           32              jmp int10_end
00527                       000001D7            int10_test_vbe_06:
00528 01D7           3C                     06    cmp al, #0x06
00529 01D9           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_07
00530 01DB           E8         9C16              call vbe_biosfn_set_get_logical_scan_line_length
00531 01DE           EB           29              jmp int10_end
00532                       000001E0            int10_test_vbe_07:
00533 01E0           3C                     07    cmp al, #0x07
00534 01E2           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_08
00535 01E4           E8         9C5A              call vbe_biosfn_set_get_display_start
00536 01E7           EB           20              jmp int10_end
00537                       000001E9            int10_test_vbe_08:
00538 01E9           3C                     08    cmp al, #0x08
00539 01EB           75           05              jne int10_test_vbe_0A
00540 01ED           E8         9C7F              call vbe_biosfn_set_get_dac_palette_format
00541 01F0           EB           17              jmp int10_end
00542                       000001F2            int10_test_vbe_0A:
00543 01F2           3C                     0A    cmp al, #0x0A
00544 01F4           75           05              jne int10_normal
00545 01F6           E8         9CAE              call vbe_biosfn_return_protected_mode_interface
00546 01F9           EB           0E              jmp int10_end
00547                       000001FB            int10_normal:
00548 01FB           06                           push es
00549 01FC           1E                           push ds
00550 01FD           60                           pusha
00551                                           ;; We have to set ds to access the right data segment
00552 01FE           BB                   C000    mov bx, #0xc000
00553 0201           8EDB                         mov ds, bx
00554 0203           E8         3495              call _int10_func
00555 0206           61                           popa
00556 0207           1F                           pop ds
00557 0208           07                           pop es
00558                       00000209            int10_end:
00559 0209           9D                           popf
00560 020A           CF                           iret
00561                                           ! 379 endasm

36441                       000090B0            vesa_pm_start:
36442 90B0                      0014              dw vesa_pm_set_window - vesa_pm_start
36443 90B2                      004B              dw vesa_pm_set_display_start - vesa_pm_start

36445 90B6                      0008              dw vesa_pm_io_ports_table - vesa_pm_start

36450 90BE                      01D0              dw 0x01CF + 1

36454                       000090C4            vesa_pm_set_window:
36455 90C4     66    83FB                   00    cmp bx, #0x00
36456 90C8           74           05              je vesa_pm_set_display_window1
36457 90CA     66    B8                   0100    mov ax, #0x0100
36458 90CE           C3                           ret
36459                       000090CF            vesa_pm_set_display_window1:
36460 90CF     66    89D0                         mov ax, dx
36461 90D2     66    52                           push dx
36462 90D4     66    50                           push ax
36463 90D6     66    BA                   01CE    mov dx, # 0x01CE
36464 90DA     66    B8                   0005    mov ax, # 0x5
36465 90DE     66    EF                           out dx, ax
36466 90E0     66    58                           pop ax
36467 90E2     66    BA                   01CF    mov dx, # 0x01CF
36468 90E6     66    EF                           out dx, ax
36469 90E8     66    ED                           in ax, dx
36470 90EA     66    5A                           pop dx
36471 90EC     66    39C2                         cmp dx, ax
36472 90EF           75           05              jne illegal_window
36473 90F1     66    B8                   004F    mov ax, #0x004f
36474 90F5           C3                           ret
36475                       000090F6            illegal_window:
36476 90F6     66    B8                   014F    mov ax, #0x014f
36477 90FA           C3                           ret
36478                       000090FB            vesa_pm_set_display_start:
36479 90FB           80FB                   80    cmp bl, #0x80
36480 90FE           74           0A              je vesa_pm_set_display_start1
36481 9100           80FB                   00    cmp bl, #0x00
36482 9103           74           05              je vesa_pm_set_display_start1
36483 9105     66    B8                   0100    mov ax, #0x0100
36484 9109           C3                           ret
36485                       0000910A            vesa_pm_set_display_start1:
36486                                           ; convert offset to (X, Y) coordinate
36487                                           ; (would be simpler to change Bochs 1 API...)
36488 910A           50                           push eax
36489 910B           51                           push ecx
36490 910C           52                           push edx
36491 910D           56                           push esi
36492 910E           57                           push edi
36493 910F           C1E2                   10    shl edx, #16
36494 9112           81E1             0000FFFF    and ecx, #0xffff
36495 9118           09D1                         or ecx, edx
36496 911A           C1E1                   02    shl ecx, #2
36497 911D           89C8                         mov eax, ecx
36498 911F           50                           push eax
36499 9120     66    BA                   01CE    mov dx, # 0x01CE
36500 9124     66    B8                   0006    mov ax, # 0x6
36501 9128     66    EF                           out dx, ax
36502 912A     66    BA                   01CF    mov dx, # 0x01CF
36503 912E     66    ED                           in ax, dx
36504 9130         0FB7C8                         movzx ecx, ax
36505 9133     66    BA                   01CE    mov dx, # 0x01CE
36506 9137     66    B8                   0003    mov ax, # 0x3
36507 913B     66    EF                           out dx, ax
36508 913D     66    BA                   01CF    mov dx, # 0x01CF
36509 9141     66    ED                           in ax, dx
36510 9143         0FB7F0                         movzx esi, ax
36511 9146           58                           pop eax
36512 9147           83FE                   04    cmp esi, #4
36513 914A           74           17              jz bpp4_mode
36514 914C           83C6                   07    add esi, #7
36515 914F           C1EE                   03    shr esi, #3
36516 9152         0FAFCE                         imul ecx, esi
